Description: WPS 文档朗读助手 for ARM64 Kylin
 Developer: Zhang Jingyao. Release date: 20260517.
 Supports ARM64 麒麟操作系统 and WPS Office 2023 for Linux / WPS Office 2019 for Linux.
 Provides a WPS JS add-in and local offline TTS daemon. The daemon listens
 only on 127.0.0.1 and uses a bundled Sherpa-onnx VITS fanchen-C Chinese
 model for clear offline read-aloud with lightweight English preprocessing.
